title: Continue 10,000 $JAMM/month salary for Brian
body:
I propose that we continue to pay 10,000 $JAMM to Brian as Lead Tinkerer for Jamm. Note that Brian will also be paid 1.26 million $JAMM (vested) in November 2022. To change Brian's salary, we need an equal or higher quorum than the initial proposal: https://snapshot.page/#/jamm/proposal/QmWqULh65TX5DgV5iPTGKtUE3tRkX8W8qS8oVup42HMrkT.

Proposer: Shreyas, Discord HelloShreyas#2656
Recipient: Brian, Discord bflynn#4073
Recipient Address: flynnjamm.eth
Budget Category: Lead Tinkerer Salary
Payment Date: Dec 1
choices: Yes, keep Brian's salary the same
